Package: python3-pineapple
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: docker.io
Description: Smart framework detection, Dockerfile generation & container builds
 Scans any project directory, detects the framework and language,
 and generates a production-ready multi-stage Dockerfile — zero
 dependencies, pure Python stdlib.
 .
 Features:
  * 23+ frameworks detected (Next.js, Vite, Django, FastAPI, Go, Rust, etc.)
  * Package manager aware (pnpm, yarn, npm)
  * Multi-stage Dockerfiles for lean production images
  * Build support — automatically build the image after generation
  * Docker daemon verification via 'pineapple verify docker'
